# Skills: single source of truth

- **All Agent Skills for this project live in `.cursor/skills/`.** There are no other skill folders in the repo.
- When adding, editing, or updating a skill (SKILL.md or any file under a skill folder), make changes **only** in `.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/`.
- Do not create or edit skills in any other path (e.g. no `skills/` folders under other project directories).
